THE NATION IS WATCHING.

13:00.079 --> 13:00.712
[ MOANING ]

13:00.779 --> 13:03.315
AS A STUDENT BODY
ARE BETTER THAN THIS.

13:03.382 --> 13:08.187
AND SO I ASK YOU AS YOUR DEAN
TO TURN AWAY FROM --

13:08.254 --> 13:12.025
I FORGOT HOW MUCH I LIKE YOU
AFTER A BIG WIN.

13:12.091 --> 13:13.960
