WE EVER GOT ALONG.

13:14.026 --> 13:16.128
[ LAUGHS ]
THAT´S TRUE.

13:18.564 --> 13:22.201
YOU KNOW,
I HAD A HEART ATTACK LAST WEEK.

13:22.268 --> 13:24.237
I KNOW.

13:24.303 --> 13:25.972
