13:35.514 --> 13:37.884
[ LAUGHING ]

13:39.085 --> 13:40.887
[ POUNDING,
INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

13:44.090 --> 13:45.091
[ SCREAMS ]

13:50.829 --> 13:52.064
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

13:52.131 --> 13:53.265
IT´S THE LEADER.

13:53.332 --> 13:54.133
-THE LEADER!
-THE LEADER!

13:54.200 --> 13:56.402
-THE LEADER´S HERE.
-LEADER?

13:58.470 --> 14:00.405
OH, SHIT.

