14:18.090 --> 14:19.458
I´VE GOT ENOUGH TEAR GAS
AND TASERS

14:19.525 --> 14:20.793
TO GET YOU TO THE WHITE HOUSE.

14:20.860 --> 14:22.294
BUT WHY SHOULD I?

14:22.361 --> 14:23.529
YOU GUYS DIDN´T NEED ME
EARLIER TODAY.

14:23.595 --> 14:24.964
OH, COME ON!

14:25.031 --> 14:26.933
WHAT´S IT GONNA TAKE?

14:26.999 --> 14:29.869
I´LL NEVER PLAY A DOWN AT B.M.S.
EVER AGAIN. HOW ABOUT THAT?

14:29.936 --> 14:32.238
I WANT THAT GAME BALL.

14:32.304 --> 14:34.406
WHAT?
NO WAY.

14:34.473 --> 14:35.908
MOVE OUT!

14:35.975 --> 14:38.410
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

14:38.477 --> 14:41.813
HOLD ON! HOLD ON! HOLD ON!

14:41.881 --> 14:44.516
LOOK, I´LL -- I´LL GET YOU
SOMETHING BETTER, HUH?

14:44.583 --> 14:47.153
YEAH, IF YOU HELP ME SAVE SAMMY
AND THE GOAT HOUSE,

14:47.219 --> 14:49.088
THE PAPERS
AREN´T GONNA SAY ANYTHING

14:49.155 --> 14:50.356
ABOUT GAME BALLS TOMORROW.

14:50.422 --> 14:53.858
NO, THE HEADLINES
ARE GONNA READ, "GOATS 12-0.

14:53.926 --> 14:56.461
RADON RANDELL SAVES THE DAY."

15:02.134 --> 15:05.570
YOU LUCKY I RIOTED
ALL MY ANGER OUT.

15:07.639 --> 15:09.074
I´LL DO IT.

15:09.141 --> 15:11.076
