AND BANG MY BROTHER.

15:44.376 --> 15:45.577
OKAY.

15:45.644 --> 15:49.215
GO, GO, GO.

15:49.281 --> 15:50.349
THANK YOU.

15:50.416 --> 15:53.119
YOU CAN THANK ME
WHEN YOU´RE DONE LAYING PIPE.

15:57.023 --> 16:00.159
WHEN I WAS 24 YEARS OLD,
I HAD NO IDEA THAT THIS --

16:00.226 --> 16:01.194
12-0!

16:01.260 --> 16:02.461
FOR GOD´S SAKES!

16:02.528 --> 16:03.329
WHOO!

16:04.330 --> 16:05.331
[ GRUNTS ]

16:05.397 --> 16:06.665
YOU´RE PRETTY GOOD AT THIS.

16:06.732 --> 16:07.666
I´M FROM DETROIT.

16:07.733 --> 16:09.668
