16:12.004 --> 16:13.438
UH, FROM A POLICE OFFICER.

16:14.173 --> 16:15.574
HARMON!

16:15.641 --> 16:17.143
-STOP THE CART!
-NO, NO, NO, NO.

16:17.209 --> 16:19.178
YOU GOT TO KEEP GOING.
YOU GOT TO KEEP GOING, MAN.

16:19.245 --> 16:21.180
IF WE STOP, IT´S OVER.
GO, GO, GO, GO!

16:21.247 --> 16:24.250
GO!
SAVE THE GOAT HOUSE!

16:24.316 --> 16:25.985
SAVE THE DRUGS!

16:26.052 --> 16:27.353
[ SCREAMING ]

16:27.419 --> 16:29.454
LET´S GO, BITCHES.

16:31.323 --> 16:33.592
♪ WHAT YOU GONNA SAY NOW? ♪

16:33.659 --> 16:35.128
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

16:38.730 --> 16:41.300
♪ WHAT YOU GONNA SAY NOW? ♪

16:41.367 --> 16:42.601
AAH!

16:42.668 --> 16:44.370
THAT´S MY TIT!

16:44.436 --> 16:46.205
[ SHOUTING CONTINUES ]

16:46.272 --> 16:49.408
♪ WHAT YOU GONNA SAY NOW? ♪

16:49.475 --> 16:51.110
HURRY, SAMMY!

16:51.177 --> 16:53.146
ALL RIGHT,
YOU TWO ARE KISSING EACH OTHER

16:53.212 --> 16:55.081
AT THE END OF THE BED,
STARING AT ME.

16:55.147 --> 16:57.516
YOU, YOU´RE IN THE CORNER
