17:12.164 --> 17:15.067
YOU TWO, START KISSING EACH
OTHER AT THE END OF THE BED.

17:15.134 --> 17:16.668
YOU, GET IN THE CORNER
AND START TOUCHING YOURSELF.

17:16.735 --> 17:18.970
AND YOU TWO, GET ON TOP OF ME.

17:19.038 --> 17:21.040
THE REST OF YOU,
JUST FILL IN WHERE YOU SEE FIT.

17:21.107 --> 17:22.408
AND ACTION.

17:25.644 --> 17:28.714
♪ WHAT YOU GONNA SAY NOW? ♪

17:29.448 --> 17:31.050
[ SCREAMS ]

17:31.117 --> 17:32.618
[ GIRLS SCREAMING ]

17:32.684 --> 17:36.088
♪ WHAT YOU GONNA SAY NOW? ♪

17:41.327 --> 17:43.162
[ DOOR OPENS ]

17:43.229 --> 17:45.030
[ PANTING ]

17:45.097 --> 17:47.299
THEY´RE ANIMALS.

17:47.366 --> 17:49.501
MARTY...

17:49.568 --> 17:52.104
YOU´VE GOT TO TALK TO THEM.

17:52.171 --> 17:53.605
THEY RESPECT YOU.

17:53.672 --> 17:55.374
YOU CAN PUT A STOP TO THIS.

17:55.441 --> 17:56.742
GET ON YOUR KNEES.

17:56.808 --> 17:57.709
EXCUSE ME?

17:57.776 --> 18:01.247
