TO THIS RIOT?

18:09.121 --> 18:10.322
LET ME THINK ABOUT IT.

18:12.091 --> 18:13.359
WAIT A SECOND.

18:13.425 --> 18:14.793
WHERE´S DEBRA?

18:22.434 --> 18:26.405
