22:15.100 --> 22:18.604
BEFORE REDEMPTION
CAN BE TRULY EARNED.

22:18.670 --> 22:20.472
THANK YOU.

22:20.539 --> 22:21.707
YEAH!

22:21.773 --> 22:24.343
WHOO!
I DID IT! I DID IT!

22:24.410 --> 22:26.845
ALEX!
MARY JO!

22:26.912 --> 22:29.648
♪ IT WENT TOO FAR ♪

22:29.715 --> 22:30.916
OH, MY GOD.

22:30.982 --> 22:33.985
SAMMY, UH, WE WERE GONNA TELL
YOU, I SWEAR TO GOD.

22:35.020 --> 22:36.121
YES!

22:37.489 --> 22:39.057
-YES!
-YEP, OKAY.

22:39.124 --> 22:41.394
OH, THIS IS GREAT.

22:41.460 --> 22:43.962
